SCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001675_183396573615106_2241025425633465028_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Y2AHqoBOo4AQ7kNvgEP35B_&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB7L8Qzsn2pkg38wVP54cnMODc6eSIJQSCkrMx8XdLS8A&oe=66D6F66D"}]}, "id": "499748217906858", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "scrshts_0001_Layer-4.png", "id": "927688834648355", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982586_927688837981688_3492050327686788621_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Bv2_clVsO7EQ7kNvgF9bUjo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCCn8gpRJjrrcfKA45sAzIHZa-PLPMKMiqPlJW5-2mSYg&oe=66D6FEED"}, {"file_name": "scrshts_0000_Layer-5.png", "id": "922582825173596", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031567_922582828506929_5296870872997217138_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FhoRtgVrfccQ7kNvgEe5xWE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDGhDJS0S0Lcza68_mHw6_csYl5IIBgG0eIBWjRrusIZQ&oe=66D6F6C5"}, {"file_name": "scrshts_0003_Layer-2.png", "id": "777617422887584", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001663_777617426220917_5046911845590742222_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=onjRUzss6CkQ7kNvgH8vzPg&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCtx2gU55X--9kHKx_fCrB-RpNsuxW3xR95zKZnvqumjw&oe=66D6FCC1"}, {"file_name": "scrshts_0004_Layer-1.png", "id": "522467975409751", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974909_522467978743084_3999197066674584349_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4GmXwArETjEQ7kNvgG9TqwM&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBks4B33njtGu1xemHu9MSaf8GyOBWzh25fKf9Mu8qwCw&oe=66D6EE66"}, {"file_name": "scrshts_0002_Layer-3.png", "id": "299838361722592", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982602_299838365055925_766843420144144362_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vupUykgw7MYQ7kNvgG0qLTo&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBcJvob6E6NE4ucZRJBRiiXbd2J9AC-G2MagSutgD9fyA&oe=66D70486"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "duct1.png", "id": "1397415597298549", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974721_1397415600631882_7348845150561262811_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Rjpwy2xEa1MQ7kNvgHrdtG7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAPEEq_vRd5_FJTG0hxy2elgNwB06t20GACpGVV6qEkpA&oe=66D6EBCD"}, "display_name": "Fetal Heart VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Fetal Heart VR is a self-teaching tool to learn geometry, anatomy, and function of Congenital Heart Diseases.\n\nWith the app, you can make a virtual ultrasound scan of normal and abnormal heart models and learn specific anatomical and geometrical features typical for Congenital Heart Diseases. The controller simulates the ultrasound probe - by moving it like an ultrasound probe you can obtain all recommended fetal cardiac views for prenatal examination\n\nWith the Fetal Heart VR, we hope to enable a more personal, affordable opportunity to learn how to perform ultrasound scans, available for all professionals involved in prenatal sonography.\n\nThis version includes a healthy fetal heart as well as 14 Congenital Heart Defects: tetralogy of Fallot (TOF), Transposition of the Great Arteries (dTGA, lTGA),  hypoplastic left heart syndrome (HLHS MS-AA, HLHS MAAA), Critical Aortic Stenosis (CritAS), Atrio-Ventricular Septal Defect (AVSD, uAVSD) Double Outlet Right Ventricle (DORV) and more.", "short_description": "Fetal Heart VR is a self-teaching tool to learn geometry, anatomy, and function of Congenital Heart Diseases.\nWith the app, you can make a virtual ultrasound scan of normal and abnormal heart models and learn specific anatomical features typical for Congenital Heart Diseases. The controller simulates the ultrasound probe - by moving it like an ultrasound probe you can obtain all recommended fetal cardiac views for prenatal examination."}]}, "developer_name": "MWU Software", "developer_privacy_policy_url": 